contactGroupId

protected SWIGTYPE_p_dJointGroupID contactGroupId

deleted

protected boolean deleted
Flag indicating that this world has been requested to be deleted. After this is set to true, none of the methods should allow further calls to ODE as the values are invalid, and may well cause a crash of the library or other strange error.

setMaxContactGeomsPerNearcallback

public void setMaxContactGeomsPerNearcallback(int size)
Sets how many contact geoms will be generated per dCollide (nearCallback) call. Smaller values make simulation faster, larger values better simulation. Default size is 12.

Parameters:
size -
